Replaces the EAN13 field on products, partners and packaging by a field
with the same technical name that accepts EAN13, EAN8, JPC, UPC and GTIN.

===========

`feedback <https://github.com/OCA/stock-logistics-barcode/issues/new?body=module:%20product_gtin%0Aversion:%2013.0%0A%0A**Steps%20to%20reproduce**%0A-%20...%0A%0A**Current%20behavior**%0A%0A**Expected%20behavior**>`_.
